        "type": "paragraph",
        "id": "179a7d5a-880b-40cb-8aa6-cf55361a9a86",
        "text": "[[Single sign-on]] (SSO) systems allow a single user [[authentication]] process across multiple IT systems or even organizations. SSO is a subset of federated identity management, as it relates only to authentication and technical interoperability."
      },
      "after": "d4038f34-1038-4dd8-b315-a609f4bc8418",
      "id": "179a7d5a-880b-40cb-8aa6-cf55361a9a86",
